      <item>
        <title>Buff Aristocrat&#39;s Double-Vote</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Htm]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Nice ability but I feel like it could be used to decide whether a person is noble or aristo and it could also out aristo being in game if people who abstained had their vote turned to pardon/execute.</p>
<p>Examples:</p>
<p>Prince: Hey 8  you claimed noble right?</p>
<p>8 (Converted Noble): Yeah I did</p>
<p>Prince: Use noble twin then or instant execute.</p>
<p><em>Fails to use noble twin instantly dead</em></p>
<hr>
<p>Abstainer: my vote turned into pardon! we have an aristo</p>
<p>Abstainer 2: Mine too</p>
<p>Abstainer 3: Same here.</p>
          <p><a href="https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/buff-aristocrats-double-vote/71072/2">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
