        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Shrimpy]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <blockquote>
<p><strong>Rabble-Rouse (Day ability)</strong> - Change all abstain votes to execute if you voted execute, or pardon if you voted pardon. (2 use)</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I think this would make Aristocrat significantly stronger and funner to play.</p>
